high_descs: Turn to your right and go forward until you come to the stove, then turn left to face the counter at the left edge of the stove.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and go to face the microwave above the sink at the opposite wall.
Place the tomato in the microwave, cook it and remove it from the microwave.
Turn around and to to the fridge behind you.
Open the fridge, place the tomato to the left of the platter on the lower shelf and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwave cooked tomato in the fridge.
